c: 4
v: 173
t: "Ke kwabo bakholwayo benze imisebenzi elungileyo, Yena Uya kubanika umvuzo wabo oyimfanelo yabo (Abanike) ngakumbiokuvelakwiziBelezaKhe. Kebonaabobangafuniyo ukuMnqula Yena, bekhukhumele nokukhukhumala Uza kubohlwaya ngesona sohlwayo sakha sabuhlungu yaye abayi kufumana bani ngaphandle koAllâh oya kuba ngumkhuseli okanye umncedi"